============


4️⃣ Strides = 2
strides=2

Filter movement:

moves 2 pixels each step

Example:

Without stride:
⬜⬜⬜⬜⬜

With stride=2:

skips faster across image

Benefit:

reduces computation
faster processing

==============


5️⃣ Padding = 'same'
padding='same'

Padding adds extra borders around image.

Purpose:

preserve image size
avoid losing edge information

Two types:

| Type  | Meaning                          |
| ----- | -------------------------------- |
| same  | Output size almost same as input |
| valid | No extra padding                 |


===============

6️⃣ Activation = ReLU
activation='relu'

ReLU means:

f(x)=max(0,x)

f(x)=max(0,x)

Purpose:

converts negative values to 0
helps CNN learn complex patterns

